<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Code de verification FinTrust</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f4f8ff;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#0f172a;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background:#f4f8ff;padding:32px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="max-width:640px;background:#ffffff;border-radius:24px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(21,96,189,.12);">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:32px 40px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e3a8a,#3b82f6);color:#ffffff;">
              <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:28px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:800;">FinTrust</h1>
              <p style="margin:10px 0 0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;opacity:.92;">Verification securisee de votre adresse e-mail</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:36px 40px;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;">Bonjour {{ user.getFullName() }},</p>
              <p style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;">
                Votre compte FinTrust a bien ete cree. Utilisez le code suivant pour finaliser votre inscription :
              </p>

              <div style="margin:0 0 24px;padding:18px 22px;border-radius:16px;background:#eff6ff;border:1px solid #bfdbfe;text-align:center;">
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1d4ed8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-bottom:10px;">
                  Code de verification
                </div>
                <div style="font-size:36px;letter-spacing:8px;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;">{{ code }}</div>
              </div>

              <p style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#475569;">
                Ce code expire le {{ expiresAt|date('d/m/Y') }} a {{ expiresAt|date('H:i') }}.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 28px;text-align:center;">
                <a href="{{ loginUrl }}" style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 24px;border-radius:14px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e3a8a,#3b82f6);color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;">
                  Acceder a FinTrust
                </a>
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#475569;">
                Si vous n etes pas a l origine de cette inscription, ignorez simplement cet e-mail.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#0f172a;">
                L equipe FinTrust
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
